CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, September 26, 1959, pg. A8 reads: Time Out For Planning - Members of Iota Chapter of Alpha Kappa Alpha Sorority of the University of Pittsburgh take time out from their busy study schedule to plan for their annual barn dance which will be held at North Park, Sept. 25. Left to right, first row: Joan Clark, Andrea Jones, Vinnie Haddock and Connie Cottingham.  Second row: Mae Louise Allen, Sara Blakey and Shirley Mike. Third row: Frances Pace, Norma Boyde and Loretta White. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Alpha Kappa Alpha members, from left, first row: Joan Clark, Andrea Jones, Vinnie Haddock, and Connie Cottingham; second row: Mae Louise Allen, Sara Blakey, and Shirley Mike; third row: Frances Pace, Norma Boyde, and Loretta White, posed on lawn at University of Pittsburgh
